<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202111/23/P2021112300262.htm |title=教育局宣布龍翔官立中學與九龍工業學校合併 |publisher=政府公報 |access-date=2021-11-23 |archive-date=2021-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210125555/https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202111/23/P2021112300262.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並與各辦學團體商討將部分收生不足的學校停辦<ref>{{cite news|url=https://topick.hket.com/article/3080383/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B5%81%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%91%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85%E6%96%99%E8%B6%85%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E3%80%80%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E8%88%87%E8%BE%A6%E5%9C%98%E5%95%86%E5%81%9C%E8%BE%A6%E5%80%8B%E5%88%A5%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E4%B8%A6%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%98%E6%A0%A1%E6%A8%B9%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3|title=【學生流失】未來數年學童跌幅料超估算　教育局與辦團商停辦個別學校並率先殺官校樹榜樣|work=Topick!|date=2021-10-02|accessdate=2021-11-23|archive-date=2021-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211123142733/https://topick.hket.com/article/3080383/%E3%80%90%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%B5%81%E5%A4%B1%E3%80%91%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E6%95%B8%E5%B9%B4%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E8%B7%8C%E5%B9%85%E6%96%99%E8%B6%85%E4%BC%B0%E7%AE%97%E3%80%80%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E8%88%87%E8%BE%A6%E5%9C%98%E5%95%86%E5%81%9C%E8%BE%A6%E5%80%8B%E5%88%A5%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E4%B8%A6%E7%8E%87%E5%85%88%E6%AE%BA%E5%AE%98%E6%A0%A1%E6%A8%B9%E6%A6%9C%E6%A8%A3|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是為第三次「-{zh-hant:殺校;zh-hans:杀校;}-潮」。

